events.name: 放蕩貴族からの依頼自動実行

parameters:
Clea: For a residence of the Senate, it's quite modest,
isn't it?

Maid Amina: Lady Pilia doesn't prefer flashy things, huh...
I wish our master would learn a little from her.

Thief Nora: Um, what kind of person is Lady Pilia? The queen
is Lady Caron, right? And who is this Lord Leucos?

Maid Amina: It's quite complicated... Queen Leucos was the
first queen of King Agnos, the handsome king.

Maid Amina: Lady Pilia is the younger brother of Lord
Leucos.

Maid Amina: Lord Leucos, who had a weak body, passed away
early. King Agnos remarried, and Lady Caron became the
second queen.

Maid Amina: Afterwards, King Agnos passed away during the
Second Tarasa War.

Maid Amina: Since Lady Caron also gave birth to a son, there
are currently two heirs to the throne, and it remains
vacant.

Thief Nora: Huh, it's quite complicated... It's also strange
that the first prince didn't become the king!
Maid Amina: There are various complicated backgrounds--

Senate Member Pilia: That voice is definitely Amina, isn't
it? I wonder if Luid is not with her today?

Maid Amina: Long time no see, Master. He is currently at the
palace delivering tribute gifts.

Maid Amina: Today, in order to solve Lady Pilia's concerns,
we have come to the adventurer's guild, Ftera.

Senate Member Pilia: Your master is too considerate. Let's
discuss your concerns inside.

Senate Member Pilia: Everyone, please come up to the second
floor of the mansion.

Maid Amina: Lady Pilia is a very friendly person, but please
make sure not to be rude under any circumstances.

Royal Court Official Emoni: Haa... Haa... I can't believe it
has come to this...

Royal Court Official Emoni: Ugh, oh no... Ugh... I can't
believe people are being killed so easily...

Royal Court Official Emoni: I will fight against them... I
will have to fight against them... against that monster...

Royal Court Official Emoni: W-Why, how did it come to
this...

Royal Court Official Emoni: Haa... Haa... I have to go back
and report this to Lady Caron...
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
